name: APE DAO REMIX! #2683
description:
APE DAO REMIX! Project is a collection of 5,550 NFTs derived from the first 50 BAYC NFTs that were 

the genesis of APE DAO. Each of the DAO's Apes was remixed by some of the hottest NFT artists in the 

community. There are 111 editions of each Remix in the collection and each NFT includes membership 

to the exclusive APE DAO community.
